00:10:37.830 --> 00:10:38.620
DIO!

00:10:39.200 --> 00:10:41.090
It's been eleven seconds.

00:10:41.090 --> 00:10:43.540
I guess that's your limit now.

00:10:44.700 --> 00:10:46.050
What?!

00:10:47.640 --> 00:10:51.260
