00:12:35.810 --> 00:12:39.600
The moment you've healed,
I'll throw Star Platinum at you.

00:12:39.600 --> 00:12:40.950
So bring it on!

00:12:42.260 --> 00:12:45.000
If I were a gunslinger in a Western, I'd say...

00:12:46.150 --> 00:12:51.070
"Draw. Let's see who's
the fastest gun in the West."

00:12:54.660 --> 00:12:56.170
H-He's...

00:12:56.680 --> 00:12:58.930
