00:13:28.560 --> 00:13:30.960
I, DIO, have no such thoughts.

00:13:30.960 --> 00:13:35.060
Within my mind is but one simple thought.

00:13:35.060 --> 00:13:36.630
Just one!

00:13:36.630 --> 00:13:40.260
To be victorious and rule! That is all.

00:13:40.260 --> 00:13:42.470
That is all I need to feel satisfaction!

00:13:43.000 --> 00:13:45.990
How I do it...

00:13:45.990 --> 00:13:48.850
