00:19:22.880 --> 00:19:25.980
This is Car Two. It's amazing!

00:19:25.980 --> 00:19:27.740
Mr. Joestar has woken up!

00:19:28.410 --> 00:19:30.730
Mr. Joestar has come back from the dead!

