Hooray! Over!

00:19:34.420 --> 00:19:38.030
Now you've returned what you took from us,

00:19:38.760 --> 00:19:39.750
DIO.

00:20:08.990 --> 00:20:11.040
Now, it's over.

00:20:16.500 --> 00:20:19.500
So many people lent something to DIO.

00:20:19.500 --> 00:20:22.370
Many people, for the last hundred years.

00:20:23.190 --> 00:20:25.840
They lent him everything.

00:20:26.860 --> 00:20:29.830
And too many of those things
will never be returned.

00:20:30.780 --> 00:20:35.510
Yeah. The things we can't get back
are too numerous, and too great.

00:20:36.860 --> 00:20:41.790
What we've lost is as vast
as the planet Earth itself.

00:20:42.310 --> 00:20:44.740
But it's all because of them...

00:20:44.740 --> 00:20:48.010
It's because of them that we still live.

00:20:51.240 --> 00:20:52.220
Kakyoin.

00:20:52.710 --> 00:20:53.570
Iggy.

00:20:54.500 --> 00:20:55.650
Avdol.

00:20:57.370 --> 00:20:58.460
It's over.

00:21:08.560 --> 00:21:11.710
Are you really going back to France, Polnareff?

00:21:12.660 --> 00:21:14.840
You don't have any more family there, do you?

00:21:14.840 --> 00:21:18.130
Why don't you come to New York with me?

00:21:20.680 --> 00:21:25.310
Mr. Joestar, even though my family
is gone, France is my homeland.

00:21:25.900 --> 00:21:27.920
I have many memories in my hometown.

00:21:27.920 --> 00:21:30.820
No matter where I go,
I'll always return there.

00:21:31.580 --> 00:21:33.550
But if you ever need me, give me a call.

00:21:33.550 --> 00:21:36.240
Wherever in the world you are,
I'll come running.

00:21:37.700 --> 00:21:38.990
It'll be lonely without you.

00:21:44.480 --> 00:21:46.700
There were many hardships,

00:21:47.590 --> 00:21:49.180
but it was a lot of fun.

00:21:49.180 --> 00:21:51.960
That journey was fun
because all of you were there.

00:21:51.960 --> 00:21:52.950
Yeah.

00:21:53.880 --> 00:21:58.420
Yes, it was fun. I believe that
from the bottom of my heart.

00:21:59.960 --> 00:22:02.440
Passengers on France International
Airlines Flight 92,

00:22:02.440 --> 00:22:05.730
bound for Paris, please head to Gate 18.

00:22:07.120 --> 00:22:10.720
Well, see ya, you shit-stained geezer!
I hope you live forever!

00:22:10.720 --> 00:22:14.230
And you, his stingy grandson!
Don't you dare forget me!

00:22:14.540 --> 00:22:15.810
Let us meet again!

00:22:15.810 --> 00:22:19.740
If you don't hate me by then,
you little jackass!

00:22:20.020 --> 00:22:23.880
I couldn't forget a guy like you if I tried.

00:22:24.540 --> 00:22:25.750
Take care.

00:22:27.760 --> 00:22:28.870
So long.

00:22:29.210 --> 00:22:30.050
Yeah.

00:22:30.520 --> 00:22:31.380
So long.

00:22:46.510 --> 00:22:47.730
Holly...

00:22:48.150 --> 00:22:50.250
Why are you sitting up all of a sudden?

00:22:50.250 --> 00:22:54.460
I... Suddenly, I feel so much better!

00:22:55.270 --> 00:22:57.380
And I just felt it in my heart...

00:22:57.380 --> 00:22:58.170
What?

00:22:58.170 --> 00:23:00.280
They're both coming home, Mama!

00:23:03.760 --> 00:23:04.540
Holly!

00:23:05.190 --> 00:23:06.750
Papa and Jotaro!

00:23:08.540 --> 00:23:10.020
They're coming home!

00:23:36.840 --> 00:23:40.030
End